{"ar":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"GUY: خلال التسعة تريليون حياة تعلمت بأن"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"الكل يعشق جمع العملات اللامعة."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"انطلق وانشر قليلًا منها في العالم!"}],"de":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"GUY: Wenn ich was gelernt habe in meinen neun Billionen Leben ..."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"... dann, dass Menschen gern glänzende Münzen sammeln."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Los, los! Verteil ein paar davon!"}],"en":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"If I learned one thing in my nine trillion lives,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"It's that people love collecting shiny coins."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Go place a few in the world!
"}],"es":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.482000000","text":"GUY: Si algo he aprendido en mis tropecientos millones de vidas,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.507000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.406000000","text":"es que a todos les encanta coleccionar monedas relucientes."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.757000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Venga, ¡puebla el mundo con ellas!"}],"es-419":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.930000000","text":"GUY: Si aprendí una cosa en mis nueve millones de millones de vidas,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.930000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.360000000","text":"es que la gente adora reunir monedas brillantes."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"¡Ve y coloca unas cuantas por el mundo!"}],"fr":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"GUY : Si j'ai appris une chose dans mes 9 trillions de vies,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"c'est que les gens adorent collectionner les pièces brillantes."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Allez, allez en mettre plein dans le décor !"}],"it":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.001000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.461000000","text":"GUY: Se ho imparato una cosa
nei miei nove trilioni di vite,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"è che la gente adora 
raccogliere monete luccicanti."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Su, va' a piazzarle in giro per il mondo!"}],"ja":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"ガイ: 9兆のライフを消費して学んだことがひとつある"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"皆ピカピカなコインが好きだってこと"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"世界へ飛び出ていくつか置いてこよう！"}],"ko":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"가이: 내가 9조 번을 살면서 배운 게 하나가 있는데"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"사람들은 반짝이는 코인 모으는 걸 좋아해"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"자, 어서 세상에 코인 몇 개를 뿌려봐!"}],"pl":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"FACET: Jeśli czegoś się nauczyłem, żyjąc dziewięć bilionów razy,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"to tego, że ludzie uwielbiają zbierać błyszczące monety."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Porozrzucaj po świecie trochę monet!
"}],"pt-br":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.709000000","text":"GUY: Se tem uma coisa que eu aprendi nos meus nove trilhões de vidas"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"é que todo mundo adora uma moeda brilhante."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Então coloque algumas moedas no mundo!"}],"ru":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.789000000","text":"ПАРЕНЬ: Вот что я понял за свои девять триллионов жизней:"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.953000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.679000000","text":"люди обожают собирать блестящие монетки."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Раскидай немного монет по миру!"}],"tr":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"GUY: Dokuz trilyon kez ölüp dirilirken
bir şey öğrendiysem;"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.146000000","text":"insanlar parlak paraları toplamayı seviyor."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"Koş, git de bunlardan yerleştir."}],"zh-CN":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.000000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.460000000","text":"你问我在九万亿次人生中学到了什么，"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.752000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.046000000","text":"那肯定是人们都喜欢收集闪亮硬币。"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.091000000","text":"去呀，在这里找到些硬币吧！"}]}
